While this scanner works on your device, using machine learning, please be aware that it is a proprietary component provided by Google, governed by this privacy policy, and that some limited telemetry might be sent back to Google’s servers to improve their software. As noted in the MLKit terms, this won’t include any information about the products you scan and the telemetry is anonymized.
